    "encrypted": "false",
    "instructions_important": "false",
    "long_instructions": "#### Snap Remix\r\n\r\nJuan is excited about a remix he made for Snap. He recognized a **pattern** in his music and used that pattern to build his remix efficiently:\r\n\r\n> It starts with two sets of beats and effects, then it explodes into three sets of bass, beats, and leads. With loops, I was able to do it with just 9 blocks!\r\n\r\n**Your task:** Identify the patterns in Juan's remix by examining the code for repeating sounds. Use loops to recreate the remix using the provided tracks. When you're finished, the timeline should look like this:\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/fca6d5ce6f4e1ba782c508cd6f4e0805-image-1741895798503.56.32 PM.png)",
    "offer_browser_tts": "true",
    "use_secondary_finish_button": "false",
    "hide_share_and_remix": "true",
